* Party travels to where they know of Thakha
* Heavy snowstorm sets in mid day
* Meet Thakha and her owlbears
* Learn of her status as former contender for leader of Galaban, that not all in the tribe align with Za'alai
* Think about getting Thakha in charge and taking out Za'
* Attacked by a scouting party of the Galaban. Victorious, no owlbear casualties
* Thakha implores them not to take further Galaban lives for the rest of their mission
* General plan is to sneak into the Galaban territory, trick or convince them into believing that Za and Ossentia don't have their best interests at heart
